{
  "id": "RAW_2386f559",
  "title": "OpenAI 给 Claude Code 做了个插件",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247514795&idx=1&sn=a31743d856ab7483e481183eedf36cc6",
  "date": "2026-03-31 07:22:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3058e6d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjXSGuwJvpdhZtuNXYibPNTwMvlOaGXOictfgsueW7R9DJssAwC4yMqDUjVQXKLZJPdkrHrWc9CeLCGDrbh2wISoLiarAQjdmialQwtP9NPfZpmY%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>OpenAI，伸出了小手手</p>\n  <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.02);padding:0;\">\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#cf4436;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">PRODUCT</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px 32px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天 OpenAI 在 GitHub 上线了&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex-plugin-cc</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，一个专门给 Claude Code 用户的 Codex 插件，Apache-2.0 协议开源</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">截至发稿，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">半天时间&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">3.2k stars</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"333\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdhDo8F7kK5SmF3fjKfzicYF76iaSQlbt1le7k0PDrvujsjcozDIbLPUk0d9Qb6wShI9ytxDOVkcV6OKLekCoQMGiadicz3G6XMYtrY/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100031142\" data-ratio=\"0.6100917431192661\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2180\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2df3acb9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhDo8F7kK5SmF3fjKfzicYF76iaSQlbt1le7k0PDrvujsjcozDIbLPUk0d9Qb6wShI9ytxDOVkcV6OKLekCoQMGiadicz3G6XMYtrY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex-plugin-cc GitHub 页面</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">cc，就是 Claude Code 的缩写</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">装好之后，你在 Claude Code 里会多出七个斜杠命令，覆盖代码审查、对抗式审查、任务委派和后台任务管理。技术上是一次标准的</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">握手协议</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：Codex 通过本地 CLI 和 app server 跟 Claude Code 对接，跑在同一台机器上，不过云端</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">四步。前置条件是 Node.js 18.18 或更高版本</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(138, 138, 130);line-height: 1.75;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub 仓库：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">github.com/openai/codex-plugin-cc</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: rgb(138, 138, 130);line-height: 1.75;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Codex 插件文档：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">developers.openai.com/codex/plugins</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 1. 添加插件市场源</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/plugin marketplace add openai/codex-plugin-cc</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 2. 安装插件</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/plugin install codex@openai-codex</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 3. 重新加载插件</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/reload-plugins</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 4. 检查 Codex 是否就绪</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:setup</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:setup</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;会检查本地有没有 Codex。如果没装且有 npm 环境，会提示自动安装。也可以手动装：</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">npm install -g @openai/codex</span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">首次使用需要登录，支持 ChatGPT 账号和 API key 两种方式：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">!codex login</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Codex 本身也有完整的插件体系，在 Codex app 里可以浏览和安装官方插件：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"357\" data-backw=\"546\" data-ratio=\"0.6546296296296297\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9dd699c2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdgr7xXXicAbiby4twYpJicdn35V4KQCShkdHr6AYSVPic7JsTIibXZe4zuEBQ9MJOO6bSO3gEH70WITnePicAr1C0dqPUuAicKdWoV15Q%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Codex Plugins 页面</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">CLI 里跑&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">/plugins</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;也可以打开插件列表：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5111111111111111\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"279\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d884c656&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhrI0OpV17iad7TNDOqRRibKXEkezdKWzg5FD1Gicv0w7OTDT06hVnhIFH9BZ8aQkNeQw0U8s74osMluddA4OL3ozEFibTdfPo2gHk%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">CLI 插件列表</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装完插件后，直接在 prompt 窗口描述任务就行：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3194444444444444\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"174\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=52fe5342&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjC4Wzuswvicujh5J0DVtXIiaZ9qqK4Y6xyAAzI5OQic87W8sDE34hTrVRaIMh6Z9EbxF8CQJX9N9hsPduRbZUJgBjVn50Ho5YnyE%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接描述任务，Codex 自动选择合适的插件</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">装好之后，你会在 Claude Code 里看到下面这七个命令，以及一个叫&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex:codex-rescue</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的子 Agent</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px 16px;\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">七个命令</span></h2>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:review</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">标准代码审查。效果和在 Codex 里直接跑&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">/review</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;一样，</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">只读不改代码</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">用来干什么：审查当前未提交的改动，或者审查整个分支跟 main 的差异</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 审查当前未提交的改动</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:review</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 审查当前分支相对于 main 的所有改动</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:review --base main</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 多文件改动建议放后台跑，审查可能需要一些时间</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:review --background</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个命令不接受自定义审查方向。想指定重点查什么，用下面的 adversarial-review</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:adversarial-review</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">对抗式审查，比 review 更挑刺。会质疑你的实现方案和设计决策：这个假设对不对？这个权衡值不值？有没有更安全或更简单的替代方案？失败了怎么办？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">用来干什么：发版前压力测试，重点检查 auth 安全、数据丢失风险、竞态条件、回滚策略这类关键区域</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 对当前改动做对抗式审查</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:adversarial-review</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 审查分支，聚焦缓存和重试的设计选择</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:adversarial-review --base main challenge whether</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; this was the right caching and retry design</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 后台跑，重点查竞态条件</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:adversarial-review --background look for race</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; conditions and question the chosen approach</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">和 review 的关键区别：adversarial-review 可以在参数后面追加</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">自然语言</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，告诉 Codex 你想让它重点质疑什么方向。同样只读不改</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">把任务交给 Codex 去做。调查一个 bug、尝试修复、继续上次的任务，或者换个更小的模型快速过一遍</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 调查测试失败原因</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue investigate why the tests started failing</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 用最小补丁修复</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue fix the failing test with the smallest safe patch</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 继续上一次的任务</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue --resume apply the top fix from the last run</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 指定模型和推理强度</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue --model gpt-5.4-mini --effort medium</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; investigate the flaky integration test</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 用 spark 模型快速过一遍</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># （映射到 gpt-5.3-codex-spark）</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue --model spark fix the issue quickly</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 后台跑</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:rescue --background investigate the regression</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">也可以不用斜杠命令，直接用自然语言委派：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ask Codex to redesign the database connection</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">to be more resilient.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">不带&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">--resume</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;也不带&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">--fresh</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;时，插件会问你要不要继续这个仓库里最近一次的 rescue 任务。不指定&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">--model</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">--effort</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;时 Codex 用自己的默认值。这类任务官方建议放后台跑</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:status</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">查看当前仓库里正在运行和最近完成的 Codex 任务</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:status</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 查看指定任务</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:status task-abc123</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:result</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">查看已完成任务的最终输出。会返回 Codex session ID，可以用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex resume&nbsp;</span><session-id></session-id></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在 Codex 里直接打开这次运行，继续工作或审查结果</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:result</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 查看指定任务</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:result task-abc123</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:cancel</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">取消正在运行的后台任务</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:cancel</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:cancel task-abc123</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 16px 32px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:setup</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">检查 Codex 安装和认证状态。也用来管理 Review Gate</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:setup</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 开启 Review Gate</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:setup --enable-review-gate</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:rgba(26,26,24,0.38);line-height:1.7;margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"># 关闭 Review Gate</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">/codex:setup --disable-review-gate</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Review Gate</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是什么：开启后，插件会在 Claude 每次响应时通过 Stop hook 自动触发一轮 Codex 审查。如果发现问题，Claude 的提交会被拦住，Claude 先改完再继续</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 8px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(207,68,54,0.06);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#cf4436;line-height:1.9;margin:0;text-align:center;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Review Gate 可能导致 Claude 和 Codex 之间形成长时间审查循环，消耗用量较快。官方建议只在你能盯着屏幕的时候开启</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">配置</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">默认模型和推理强度可以通过&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">config.toml</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;调整。比如在某个项目里固定用 gpt-5.4-mini、推理强度拉到最高：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">model = \"gpt-5.4-mini\"</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.7;\"><span leaf=\"\">model_reasoning_effort = \"xhigh\"</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">放在项目根目录的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">.codex/config.toml</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;里即可</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">配置优先级：用户级&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">~/.codex/config.toml</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;→ 项目级&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">.codex/config.toml</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（项目级需要先信任该项目）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你之前就在用 Codex，插件会直接读取已有配置和登录状态，不需要重新设置</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex-plugin-cc</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的背景是 OpenAI 上周给 Codex 加了完整的插件体系，把 Skills、App 集成和 MCP Server 打包成可安装、可分享的工作流单元。目前已有 Gmail、Google Drive、Slack、Figma、Notion 等 20 多个官方插件</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用这个插件需要 ChatGPT 订阅（含免费版）或 OpenAI API key，用量计入 Codex 使用额度</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Codex 的插件体系和 Claude Code 走的路线很像，都在做生态打包。但&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex-plugin-cc</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的方向正好反过来：把 Codex 的能力</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">主动伸进</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">了 Claude Code 的工作流里</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">「握手协议」</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 目前在开发者工具生态里的位置比较超然。据统计，GitHub 公开提交中大约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">4%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;由 Claude Code 生成，预计年底超过 20%。2026 年初至今，Claude Code 的企业订阅量翻了四倍，企业用户贡献了超过一半的收入</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 的收入结构更依赖开发者和 API 调用。据 Bloomberg 3 月报道，Anthropic 年化收入已达约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">190 亿美元</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，去年底是 90 亿，15 个月前是 10 亿。Epoch AI 的分析认为，按目前增速，Anthropic 可能在 2026 年中追平 OpenAI 的收入规模。OpenAI 的收入更多来自 ChatGPT 订阅和大客户合同，结构不太一样</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个背景下再看&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);font-size:13.5px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">codex-plugin-cc</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，一个官方 repo，Apache-2.0 协议，安装进 Claude Code 的工作流里</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 8px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(207,68,54,0.06);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#cf4436;line-height:1.9;margin:0;text-align:center;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">小手，不是很干净</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 16px 32px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"294\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdjsC5UFaXGGHEL2Ma8kodf8Y7T57Wibm2a47gVibpFftExDSEDt2ibialKudCxQTfkhgAej20zLE4YictngGNVtF2qbN3QoCqibuYP3A/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100031146\" data-ratio=\"0.5376344086021505\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"930\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf17a003&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjsC5UFaXGGHEL2Ma8kodf8Y7T57Wibm2a47gVibpFftExDSEDt2ibialKudCxQTfkhgAej20zLE4YictngGNVtF2qbN3QoCqibuYP3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2 月，印度 AI 峰会，莫迪与全球科技领袖合影</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 发布开源插件 `codex-plugin-cc`，将 Codex 的代码审查与任务委派能力直接集成至 Anthropic 的 Claude Code 工作流中。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 发布开源插件 `codex-plugin-cc`，将 Codex 的代码审查与任务委派能力直接集成至 Anthropic 的 Claude Code 工作流中。",
  "summary": "OpenAI 在 GitHub 上线了 `codex-plugin-cc` 插件，允许 Claude Code 用户通过 7 个新增的斜杠命令直接调用 OpenAI Codex 的功能。该插件涵盖了标准代码审查、对抗式审查（重点质疑设计决策）、任务委派（rescue）以及后台任务管理等核心能力。技术上通过本地 CLI 与 app server 对接，实现本地化集成。此举被视为 OpenAI 主动介入 Claude Code 这一高增长开发者工具生态的战略举措，背景是 Anthropic 在开发者工具市场的份额和收入正在快速追赶 OpenAI。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 发布 codex-plugin-cc 插件，实现与 Claude Code 的深度集成。",
      "explanation": "通过 7 个斜杠命令，用户可以在 Claude Code 环境中直接调用 Codex 的审查和任务处理能力，实现跨厂商工具的「握手」。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入「对抗式审查」（Adversarial Review）机制。",
      "explanation": "相比普通审查，该模式会主动质疑代码的设计决策、安全风险和竞态条件，并支持通过自然语言指定特定的质疑方向。"
    },
    {
      "point": "提供任务委派（Rescue）功能与 Review Gate 机制。",
      "explanation": "用户可将 Bug 调查等任务交给 Codex 处理；开启 Review Gate 后，Codex 会自动拦截并审查 Claude 的响应，形成闭环质量控制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 战略性介入竞争对手的工作流生态。",
      "explanation": "面对 Claude Code 快速增长的市场份额，OpenAI 通过开源插件形式进入 Anthropic 的优势领地，争夺开发者入口和使用额度。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "把 Codex 的能力主动伸进了 Claude Code 的工作流里。",
    "对抗式审查，比 review 更挑刺。会质疑你的实现方案和设计决策：这个假设对不对？这个权衡值不值？",
    "Review Gate 开启后，插件会在 Claude 每次响应时自动触发一轮 Codex 审查。如果发现问题，Claude 的提交会被拦住，Claude 先改完再继续。"
  ],
